China to Restrict NBA Players From Signing Deals in China, Xinhua Reports

-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 
2011-08-19T11:13:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-19/china-to-restrict-nba-players-from-signing-deals-in-china-xinhua-reports.html
The Chinese Basketball Association
said today that it will restrict the players of the  National
Basketball Association  to play in its domestic league, the
Xinhua News Agency reported.  Players under NBA contracts would not be allowed to join
Chinese clubs from next season, Xinhua said, citing Bai Xilin,
director of the league office.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Gregory Turk at 
 gturk2@bloomberg.net  